02:54:48.400 --> 02:54:52.960
[Guest]: of excluding based on multiple characteristics. And most private schools in India, at least

02:54:52.960 --> 02:54:56.680
[Guest]: the elite private schools, which kind of play in the consciousness of the policymaking class,

02:54:56.680 --> 02:55:00.040
