02:55:00.040 --> 02:55:03.520
[Guest]: everything that they do. Okay, so one place where the market metaphor breaks down is when

02:55:03.520 --> 02:55:06.640
[Guest]: a school is not actually trying to maximise market share in the first place, but trying

02:55:06.640 --> 02:55:11.640
